Source: mariadb-fractalsql
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: FractalSQLabs <ops@fractalsqlabs.io>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper-compat (= 13),
 libluajit-5.1-dev,
 libmariadb-dev,
 pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/FractalSQLabs/mariadb-fractalsql

Package: mariadb-fractalsql-v10.6
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libc6 (>= 2.38),
 libluajit-5.1-2,
 libmariadb3,
 mariadb-server-10.6 | mariadb-server (>= 10.6)
Description: Stochastic Fractal Search UDF for MariaDB 10.6
 mariadb-fractalsql registers the fractal_search() UDF, a LuaJIT-
 backed Stochastic Fractal Search optimizer that returns JSON top-k
 matches for a query vector against an inline corpus. Compiled
 against the MariaDB 10.6 UDF ABI.

